branchCategory.name: 90-ISE50, High Precision Digital Pressure Switch for Positive Pressure
branchCategory.description: <p>High precision digital pressure switch series 90-ISE50 is a standard thread type for positive pressure. 90-ISE50 is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing. 90-ISE50 is used for a wide range of fluids. The stainless steel diaphragm prevents direct contact between sensor and measured fluid.</p>
